Code Slam : The Grand Code Off (Clan Wars)
Welcome to the Clash of Clans Friendly War Registration! We are excited to organize a friendly war between two clans, featuring 32 teams. Please read the following details carefully before filling out the form: Teams & Clans: There will be 32 teams participating, divided evenly between two clans. 16 teams will join Clan A, and the remaining 16 teams will join Clan B. Matchups: Teams will be matched against opponents with the same Town Hall level. Registration Instructions: Please provide your team details and Town Hall level in the form below. You will be assigned to a clan based on your Town Hall level and team composition. Rules & Guidelines: Follow the war rules and conduct guidelines set by the organizers for a fair and enjoyable competition. Thank you for participating, and may the best clan win!
